{
	"_readme": "V22 preregistered compute-matched late-game representation control. Both arms use one zero-expanded 199/84 V18 S0 generation-10 checkpoint and collect identical generation-1 trajectories; this arm zeros append-only observation columns 188..198 before every PPO/critic loss. Pair with fair-v22-solo-macro-treatment. No solo checkpoint is promotion-eligible without held-out multiplayer, heuristic, exploiter, fairness, and human gates.",
